alerts.title: Wind Chill Advisory
alerts.description: ...WIND CHILL ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 AM CST THIS MORNING... * WHAT...Very cold wind chills expected. Expect wind chills as low as 20 below zero. * WHERE...Portions of central, east central, south central and southeast South Dakota and southwest Minnesota. * WHEN...Until 10 AM CST this morning. * ADDITIONAL DETAILS...The cold wind chills could cause frostbite on exposed skin in as little as 30 minutes.
